# Input/Output Interface

READ: - task_description: String describing the system to be built/modified - context_data: Object containing codebase context, constraints, requirements - existing_phase_graph: Optional graph from previous checklist (for continuation)

WRITE: - markdown_checklist: Structured markdown file with phases, tasks, subtasks - phase_dependency_map: JSON graph of 3D dependencies (sequential, lateral, diagonal) - transition_rules: Explicit unlocking conditions for each phase

interface_contract:
generator_consumes: [task_description, context_data]
generator_produces: [markdown_checklist, phase_dependency_map]
executor_consumes: [markdown_checklist]
executor_produces: [completed_checklist]

---

THIS CHECKLIST ENFORCES DETERMINISTIC TASK DECOMPOSITION FOR LLM EXECUTION

